snippet.title: Maneater trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
The 'shark-PG' is back. Tripewire's new trailer gives us some much-needed story details in their new action RPG where you play as a shark who savages swimming and animals alike.

Find out more details here: https://www.pcgamer.com/maneater-shark-gameplay-pc-gaming-show/
